---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Value Proposition" description="How Green Orbit Digital helps organisations leverage space-enabled solutions to drive sustainability, resilience, and impact.">

  <main class="py-8">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
      <Hero 
        title="Our Value Proposition"
        description="Helping visionary organisations communicate the power of space-enabled solutions to address sustainability challenges and drive meaningful impact." 
      />

    <!-- Core Value Proposition -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-primary-500 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white text-lg sm:text-xl">
          At Green Orbit Digital, we collaborate with visionary organisations to harness space technologies and their synergies to address sustainability challenges, build resilience, and drive climate action.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white text-lg sm:text-xl">
          Our clients need effective marketing and communication strategies to engage stakeholders, clarify complex space-enabled solutions, and overcome misconceptions about environmental responsibility.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white text-lg sm:text-xl">
          We empower organisations to communicate their sustainability commitment clearly, inspire trust, and promote adoption of innovative, long-term solutions that create measurable impact.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white text-lg sm:text-xl">
          By combining space insights with strategic storytelling, we help our clients create meaningful change within their industries and beyondâ€”unlocking the full potential of space exploration to advance sustainability, raise awareness, and foster a more equitable future.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Work With Us -->
    <section class="bg-white dark:bg-accent-500 py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Why Choose Green Orbit Digital?</h2>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white text-lg sm:text-xl list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Deep expertise in space technologies, sustainable marketing, and strategic communications.</li>
          <li>Proven ability to translate complex technical concepts into clear, compelling narratives.</li>
          <li>Commitment to measurable sustainability impact in every campaign and collaboration.</li>
          <li>Trusted partner for organisations seeking to lead responsibly and inspire change.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="w-full bg-secondary-500 py-16 text-white text-center">
      <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to amplify your impact?</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-200">Partner with us to communicate your vision, inspire trust, and drive sustainable innovation in your industry.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition text-lg sm:text-xl">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>